                                  wait {
                                    msg ("<br/>\"I'm here, Dave. I'll be here. Forever.\"<br/><br/>\"I know. Thank you, Loan. Thank you for everything.\"<br/><br/>\"You do so much and you don't even know it, don't you, Dave?\"<br/><br/>And he quickly stops holding me and goes to get the laptop. ")
